# L3: 可管理 job（新增/修改/刪除/執行），不能管理系統設定
description: L3 job management project access
context:
  project: '.*'
for:
  resource:
    - allow: [read, create]
  job:
    - allow: [read, create, update, delete, run, kill]
  node:
    - allow: [read, run]
  adhoc:
    - allow: [read, run, kill]
by:
  group: rundeck-l3

---

description: L3 system access
context:
  application: 'rundeck'
for:
  resource:
    - allow: read
  project:
    - allow: [read, configure]
by:
  group: rundeck-l3
